  "description": {
    "zh": "等等！还没完，还有Side B呢，其他7.62x51武器也有10发弹匣。你可能会讨厌它们，所以最好做好心理准备。\n\n我不认为你会想用一把配10发弹匣的FAL，但你仍然有选择，用一把配10发弹匣的M1A也可以，完成后回来，祝你好运。\n\n指定弹匣：\n - M1A 7.62x51 10发弹匣\n - SA-58 或 FAL 7.62x51 10发弹匣",
    "en": "Hold on there! We're not done, there is a second part, other 7.62x51 guns also have ten-round magazines, you're gonna hate them so you better prepare mentally.\nI don't think you would want to use a FAL with a ten-round magazine, you still have the option, but an M1A with a ten-rounder would be valid aswell, come back when you're done and good luck out there.\n\nSpecified Magazines :\n - M1A 7.62x51 10-Round Magazine\n - SA-58 / FAL 7.62x51 10-Round Magazine"
  },
